GSD.description:
objtool: Fix SEGFAULT

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v5.10.163 by commit 0af0e115ff59d638f45416a004cdd8edb38db40c. For more details please see the references link.
